HEADWORD: Assaying
<hw>As*say"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act or process of testing,
esp. of analyzing or examining metals and ores, to determine the
proportion of pure metal.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

